My facourite is my boy,{{champion:111}} 
He's a tank who has good base stats, 3 types of hard CC (two of them being point-and-click), one AoE slow and a shield for himself.

He's not the most popular, but like Leona he can be a huge CC machine that can keep the enemy ADC still for a long ass time. He has a decent good damage and trades (Due to his Shield that also gives more dmg). Only thing he lacks is heals/shields for your ADC.
